    <p>
      Hi there! 👋 I'm Xili Wang (王熙理), an undergraduate student at the <a href="https://eecs.pku.edu.cn/xxkxjsxy/Home/HOME.htm" target="_blank" data-astro-cid-fwdcsva6="">School of EECS</a>, 
      <a href="https://www.pku.edu.cn/en/" target="_blank">Peking University</a>, majoring in Applied Physics (Experimental Class of Electronic Information Science).
    </p>
    <p>
      I have a passion for Piezoelectric and Acoustic Microelectromechanical Systems (MEMS), supervised by 
      <a href="http://lulab.pku.edu.cn/" target="_blank">Prof. Yipeng Lu</a> at the 
      <a href="https://ic.pku.edu.cn/en/" target="_blank">School of Integrated Circuit</a>, Peking University.
    </p>
